<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CRUD</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/../assets/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1 class="display-4">CRUD MySQL, Express</h1>
        <p class="lead">CRUD désigne les quatre opérations de base pour la persistance des données, en particulier le
            stockage d'informations en base de données.</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>Soit : create : créer read : lire update : mettre à jour delete : supprimer</p>
        <p class="lead">
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#form" role="button">Testez-le</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Ajout Personne</h2>
                <form action="/person/ajoutPersonne" method="POST" id="form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="txtId" placeholder="Id for update" id="txtId"
                            value="<%= txtId %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="txtNom" placeholder="Votre nom" id="txtNom"
                            value="<%= txtNom %>" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="txtPrenom" placeholder="Votre prenom"
                            id="txtPrenom" value="<%= txtPrenom %>" required />
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Envoyer</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <% personList.forEach((person)=> { %>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>
                                <%= person.id %>
                            </strong>
                            <strong>
                                <%= person.nom %>
                            </strong>
                            <strong>
                                <%= person.prenom %>
                            </strong>
                            <a style="float: right;" class="btn btn-danger" href="/person/deletePersonne/<%= person.id %>">Supprimer</a>
                            <a style="float: right;" class="btn btn-success" href="/person/editPersonne/<%= person.id %>">Modifier</a>
                        </li>
                        <% }); %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="../assets/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>